Ubuntu/Debian:

sudo apt-get update
sudo apt-get install yara

Windows:

Download YARA from GitHub releases.

Add the binary to your PATH or place libyara.dll in the script directory.

Alternatively, use Chocolatey:
choco install yara

pip3 install yara-python

python3 yara_rule_generator.py

Optional: Enable Hebrew Prompts:

Edit yara_rule_generator.py and set:
USE_HEBREW = True
